NO SHOWINGS SATURDAY(12/30) THROUGH MONDAY (1/1). Solid masonry home located in East Tucson.The front entry to the home has a welcoming courtyard.Inside the home you will find beautiful plantation shutters in the great room. New paint, brand new carpeting along with ceramic tile. Four bedrooms and two bathrooms.The recently updated kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. This home boasts an abundance of storage, inside and out!Enjoy the private backyard with sparkling pool and Hot tub!No neighbors on two sides of the property.The west side of the house is equipped with electric security shutters.The garage is equipped with a separate 80 amp sub panel with 240 electric.There is an extra storage or workshop option on the side of the garage Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants and medical services.
Home is ready for you to add your personal touch!
